name: 2 Pak Special Yellow: Star Warrior / Frogger
overview: Grey-market compilation featuring two Parker Brothers titles, a renamed version of "Star Wars: The Empire Strikes Back" (1982) and "Frogger" (1982). Box description: STAR WARRIOR You are the last of the star warriors, with battle skills famous throughout the galaxy. Your neighboring planet Treon is under a vicious monster attack and you have been asked by princess Fenia to help save the planet. Without hesitation you board your battleship to go to the rescue. Dangerous, but it could be quite rewarding. For one or two players using joysticks. FROGGER Hop your frogs across a dangerous highway, then over a raging river to the safety of home. But your frogs will have to leap away from one danger after another before they're safe. Watch out for the tricky turtles! Frog-Eating snakes and alligators! Frogger- The fast moving, quick hopping game that's full of amphibious fun. For one or two players using joysticks.
